animeDescription: A commercial for Kyary Pamyu Pamyu's collaboration with Mameshiba. The Mameshiba are unique and have legs unlike the originals.Contains:1 Rollerskating-hen (set to Kyary's Minna no Uta song)6 Ii Nikui-hen (featuring New Jersey, Missouri, Ohio, Bermuda, New York-Japanese, and Massachusetts-English as the joke/pun at the end of each episode.)1 Hatachi-hen (a clip of Kyary's Hatachi song with the new animated Mameshiba incorporated into it with new dialogue overlayed.)1 Debut-hen (a clip of Kyary's Tsukematsukeru song with the new animated Mameshiba incorporated into it with new dialogue overlayed.)
